data.description: Enjoy this charming private home with solar heated pool, fenced in back yard, Close to I-75 with easy access to Orlando & Tampa. Living room/dining room and bedrooms have pergo flooring. Master bedroom with built in closet system, updated private master bathroom. Guest bath offers tub/shower combo. Guest bedroom with 2 closets. Kitchen with island, deep sink, built in microwave, new stainless appliances, and magnetic knife holder. Indoor laundry room with additional large walk in pantry.
